window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"Go on a date with me or I'll beat up your best friend.\" A line that shouldn't have worked, but did. When your BFF is in peril, what's a girl to do?</p> <p>Jason King is used to getting what he wants. And he wants me. No clue why. I'm a geeky introvert. I must have that just-turned-eighteen, new-girl-on-the-block smell.</p> <p>Jason is popular. Cocky. His dad is richer than God. He has his crew dedicate their summer to tormenting my best friend, Donovan.</p> <p>Donovan fights back with quick tongue and a sense of humor as dark as his clothes. But he's tasted enough of Jason's knuckle-sandwiches to last a lifetime. Which is where I step in. One date with Jason and the bullying stops. It's a no-brainer.</p> <p>So I let Jason take me out for ice cream. What's the worst that can happen. Right?</p> <p>Except Jason's piercing blue eyes send a delicious shiver through me that has nothing to do with my mint chocolate-chip. Donovan is going to hate me for this.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
